<font size="2" color="#990000"><b>QUOTE OF THE DAY</b></font><br>

<font size="2">"Here you lost the most important person in your life, and
nobody gives you any recognition. You just kind of get
bypassed." <br>
<a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2002/01/22/nyregion/22FIAN.html?todaysheadlines">SUSANN BRADY,</a>whose fianc&#233;, Gavin Cushny, died at the World Trade
Center.


<hr size="1">



<font size="2" color="#990000"><b>NATIONAL</b></font><br>




<font  face="times new roman"><b><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2002/01/22/science/22ANTH.html?todaysheadlines">Scientists Report Genetic Finding That Could Aid Anthrax Inquiry</a></b><br>
Scientists say they have discovered genetic fingerprints that may help determine which laboratory is the likely source of the anthrax used in the attacks.
<P>


<font  face="times new roman"><b><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2002/01/22/politics/22DRIL.html?todaysheadlines">Agency Backs Gas Drilling at New National Monument</a></b><br>
A federal agency has found that allowing a company to drill along the Missouri River in Montana will have little environmental impact.
<P>
</font>


<font  face="times new roman"><b><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2002/01/22/national/22CYBE.html?todaysheadlines">Mayhem at Cybercafes Shakes a Town in California</a></b><br>
Gang members are descending on cafes to exact vengeance for offenses that originate on the computer screen.
<P>
</font>













<p>
